data.description: Stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home built in 2020, offering a spacious and modern living experience. Boasting 2,074 square feet, this home features an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The kitchen is a chef's dream with an oversize island adorned with granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. The master bedroom is a retreat on its own, featuring a tray ceiling, walk-in closet, and an ensuite bathroom with a double vanity and a luxurious shower. Three additional well-appointed bedrooms provide ample space for family or guests. Step outside to the fenced-in backyard and enjoy the serene view overlooking a pond, creating a perfect setting for relaxation and outdoor activities. The screened patio adds an extra layer of comfort, providing an ideal spot for enjoying the fresh air without the annoyance of bugs. Convenience is key with a dedicated laundry room and a spacious 2-car garage. This home combines elegance and functionality, offering a perfect blend of modern amenities and stylish design. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully crafted home yours. Conveniently located near the Polk Parkway, Lakeside Village, and downtown Lakeland.
